<l>Amz<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg>r m<seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>e</orig><reg>a</reg></choice></seg> yaouankiz, <seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg>m s<seg type="nasalisation"><choice><orig>on</orig><reg>oñ</reg></choice></seg>j <seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg><seg type="trigramme_diacritique"><choice><orig>h</orig><reg>c’h</reg></choice></seg> o<seg type="trigramme_diacritique"><choice><orig>h</orig><reg>c’h</reg></choice></seg> chomet. </l>     
</lg>        
<lg>
<l>Ag ur vl<seg type="nasalisation"><choice><orig>eu</orig><reg>euñ</reg></choice></seg><seg type="amuissement_consonne"><choice><reg>v</reg></choice></seg>enn d'<seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>e</orig><reg>a</reg></choice></seg>n all, evel ur bobelan
