<l>Ge<seg type="voisement"><choice><orig>d</orig><reg>t</reg></choice></seg> o li<seg type="lettre_ramiste"><choice><orig>ù</orig><reg>v</reg></choice></seg><seg type="diphtongaison"><choice><orig>eu</orig><reg>ioù</reg></choice></seg> a get
