<l><seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>E</orig><reg>A</reg></choice></seg> greden e o<seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>a</reg></choice></seg> d<seg type="monophtongaison"><choice><orig>ei</orig><reg>i</reg></choice></seg>n ; ne gaven kleu<seg type="amuissement_consonne"><choice><reg>z</reg></choice></seg>
<note n="10" resp="NC"><hi rend="i">kleuz</hi> [klø:(s)], gall. : <hi rend="i">talus</hi> (Ménard &amp; Kadored, 2001, p.749)</note> na gar<seg type="digramme_diacritique"><choice><orig>h</orig><reg>zh</reg></choice></seg>
<note n="11" resp="NC"><hi rend="i">garzh</hi> (Ménard &amp; Kadored, 2001, p.517), gall : <hi rend="i">clotûre</hi></note>
<note n="12" resp="NC"><hi rend="i">Hep kleuz na garzh</hi> (expression), bzhg : <hi rend="i">h</hi><hi rend="i">ent strizh</hi> (Ménard &amp; Kadored, 2001, p.517) ; gall. : <hi rend="i">route étroite</hi>. </note>, </l>
<l>É stl<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg>jal m’ivoul
<note n="13" resp="NC"><hi rend="i">ivoul</hi>, gall. :<hi rend="i"> volonté vive</hi>, <hi rend="i">avidité</hi> (Ernault, 1904, p.116)</note> dall, </l>
<l>Evel ur bobelan, ag ur vl<seg type="nasalisation"><choice><orig>eu</orig><reg>euñ</reg></choice></seg><seg type="amuissement_consonne"><choice><reg>v</reg></choice></seg>enn d'<seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>e</orig><reg>a</reg></choice></seg>n all. </l>     
</lg>
<pb n="6"/>       
<lg>
<l>Evel <seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>e</orig><reg>a</reg></choice></seg>r r<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg> yaouank, tai<seg type="consonne_palatalisée"><choice><orig>ll</orig><reg>lh</reg></choice></seg>et em <seg type="digramme_diacritique"><choice><orig>e</orig><reg>eu</reg></choice></seg>s <seg type="amenuisement_voyelle"><choice><orig>e</orig><reg>a</reg></choice></seg>l l<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg>z
<note n="14" resp="NC"><hi rend="i">tailhein el liz</hi>, gall. : <hi rend="i">faire la cour</hi> (Ernault, 1904, p.219)</note></l>
<l>Ha klasket karant<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg><seg type="amuissement_consonne"><choice><reg>z</reg></choice></seg>. </l>
<l>Ge<seg type="voisement"><choice><orig>d</orig><reg>t</reg></choice></seg> r<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg> a largant<seg type="signes_diacritiques"><choice><orig>é</orig><reg>e</reg></choice></seg><seg type="amuissement_consonne"><choice><reg>z</reg></choice></seg>
